name: Gateways
description:
We discovered those.

Based on our understanding of physics, those are constructs and not naturally occurring.

We believe to have mastered the Gateways, and as far as we know there are just a handful of those holes in the structure of the Universe.

They all lead to places we cannot pinpoint from Terra’s point of view on the Universe, and even with those new infinity, everything seems devoid of life.

But from time to time, without any warning, you can see the “Things” also going through those gateway. They never answer our calls, nor did we ever succeed in following them.
